item.title: CVE-2017-20145|2024-08-05T21:45:26.030Z -- tecrail -- responsive%20filemanger
item.description: A vulnerability was found in Tecrail Responsive Filemanger up to 9.10.x and classified as critical. The manipulation leads to path traversal. The attack may be launched remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used. Upgrading to version 9.11.0 is able to address this issue. It is recommended to upgrade the affected component.
